Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A frog is doing the front crawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It went to your side, so take a look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--Is that true?\N--Hey, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you taking what that\Nstupid Admiral said seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To start with, there's no way a frog\Nwould do the front cra... Hey, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A frog is doing the front crawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll follow it, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there a lighthouse in a place\Nlike that? I wonder if someone's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! The frog stopped. Corner it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran ashore on something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back! Go back! Turn 180 degrees!
