Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just turn around! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What the hell is this lump of iron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Something shaped like\Nthis can't travel on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, frog! Run! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! It got run over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship was puffing out smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma! Grandma! Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Is that true, Chimney?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, bring the Transponder Snail to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a problem.\NSomeone came out of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Err... Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... What was it? I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's drunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Paille, huh? It goes good with alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Chimney. This is our cat, Gonbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Grandma Kokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't train robbers, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Luffy. I'm the man\Nwho'll become Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,--Really?!\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What a funny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Chimney, that thing is a steamship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But with a shape like that,\Nit can't go on a voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never seen something\Nlike that, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you look all over the world,\Nthis is the only place you can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sea train called the "Puffing Tom."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Puffing Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns paddlewheels using a steam\Nengine and runs on the sea railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Railway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It runs a little\Nbelow the surface of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The train travels the same route every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,taking passengers from one island to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It carries ships and the mail as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right. There really is a railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we ran ashore on that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! There's both\Na signal and a partition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to come inside like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But the signal should face the other way.\NOtherwise, how do we see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's dangerous, that guy\Nwouldn't understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't nice to send him flying.\NWe were after him, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What? "That guy"? Are you\Ntalking about Yokozuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that front crawl frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yokozuna wouldn't die from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the source of all our\Nheadaches at this shift station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves strength contests and\Nalways tries to defeat the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll show up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength contests? Oh...\NThat's why he didn't run, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sure got guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break! We're having problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The rail guard was broken many times, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time he shows up, it causes\Nthe passengers a lot of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then! I'm not gonna eat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna eat a fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have thought about\Neating a frog in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So where do you guys wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna take the sea train from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The town of the Spring Queen, St. Poplar...\NThe gourmet town, Pucci...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Carnival town, San Faldo...\NThey're all fun places.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you work for the Government,\Nthere's a separate, special train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The gourmet town, Pucci?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the place the guys we met on the\Nuninhabited island were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll pick the gourmet town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we've got our own ship,\Nwe won't take the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just follow the log.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...? Where is it pointing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,East of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then it must be Water Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The train you saw earlier came\Nfrom that island's Blue Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the "City of Water." It's a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Water Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all, it's a city that made\Na name for itself with its shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Their technology is No. 1 in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The ships they build are the World\NGovernment's favorites! Isn't that amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Then there's gotta be\Nsome amazing shipwrights, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just "some"! It's a hangout\Nfor the world's best shipwrights!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna go there and get a\Nshipwright to join our crew for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right? Then hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,--What's that about?\N--Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then... Here's a simple map\Nof the island and a reference letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Give this to a guy named Iceberg\Nand ask him to fix your ship good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Water Seven is a big place. Don't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--Whoa!\N--Kokoro-san! You have a big heart!\NWhat a nice person you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna go back to Water Seven soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If I see you guys again, I'll treat\Nyou to a drink at my favorite bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I hope we'll see you guys again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take about a week for the log to\Nbe stored in Water Seven. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guys! Get ready to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah!\N--Well then, we'll get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all your help, Kokoro-san! Chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for the Government people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo! Let's go! To the city of meat! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... What a nice wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be able to get to the city\Nof water sooner than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, leave the shipwright search to me.\NI'll find an incredibly pretty woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?! It's a\Nshipwright we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a big guy like\Na mountain! Five meters tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he's too big, we don't know\Nif he could live okay on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All that matters is that he's skilled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, the question\Nis if we could find someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,crazy enough to want to be on a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.\NWe're gonna have another new friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We were lucky to stop at the station first,\Nsince they drew a map for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go to the place on the map\Nand visit the Iceberg guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.69,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Around here" "Water Seven"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Too simple to figure out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is like Luffy's drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:25.04,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Shipwright\NFive Meters"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're gonna all look for a guy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was a guy like that, I'd run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me, too. If I had a boat,\NI'd escape to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But this guy seems to be related to octopuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He might follow me to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you guys running on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, guys, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you some allowance for\Nthe week we're gonna stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?! Yaay! I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stand in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Allowance! Allowance! Allowance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This tinplate patchwork brings back\Nmemories of battles and adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm filled with deep emotions when I\Nthink that she will be repaired soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--I do understand that, but...\N--Hm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...especially since we entered the Grand Line, our journey has taken quite a toll on the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The deck squeaks and the leakage at\Nthe bottom of the ship is bad as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do anything, both we\Nand the ship will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we've got tons of money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have her repaired perfectly.\NWe can power her up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's get more cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's get a bronze statue on board, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The island! We can see the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, guys! Paddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got enough wind.\NDon't make us waste our energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a huge fountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! This is indeed an industrial city!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder this place has a sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... This is a lot of water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that water springing out from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting... It looks like\Nthe water comes from the fountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,goes through the canals and falls into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you wanna race on those water slides?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Race?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No! There's no way I'm doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream on, you idiot. You can't even swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nwhat do those numbers mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't know.\N--Are they walls? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet those are the entrances\Nfor the five-meter shipwrights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:19.80,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Shipwright\NFive Meters"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bunch of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The one up front must be the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It says Blue Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where the harbor is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey, you guys!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good for you pirates\Nto be openly sailing in the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go around to the backstreets over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this is amazing! A city on the water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! This place is cool! What a beautiful city!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But the city is flooded.\NThe houses are submerged in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. The city was designed\Nwith the base being submerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--Look at the foundation\Nunderneath the buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! The pillars are built higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... That's why it's called\Nthe city of water, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up and dock the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you guys!\NPirate ships shouldn't come in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you come here for?! To plunder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We wanna get our ship repaired!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Would people normally ask\Nif we're here to plunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, there's a cape ahead of here,\Nso anchor your ship there for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, right? We're pirates, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This area should be okay, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, what a dull place this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then! Furl the sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! I just pulled the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy crap! The Going Merry\Nhas gotten this rickety?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, why aren't the people\Non this island scared of pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because pirates are just\Nanother customer to their shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking and fix it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because they have\Nbodyguards strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to deal with pirates who cause a ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably do...\Nconsidering the size of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! Hey, what're we gonna do? This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would it be bad? We're customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Luffy! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we'll take the reference\Nletter from Kokoro-san
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and go find the man named Iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ask him to help us\Narrange the ship's repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have to find a place\Nwhere we can cash in our gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... All right, then! Anyway,\Nlet's go! To the city of water!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're forgetting the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Make sure you fix it good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... I somehow missed\Nthe chance to go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out together later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! I wonder if they have a bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go to the\Nmoney-changing shop first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Let's go to the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't walk around the island\Nwith this much gold. I get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after changing it to money,\Nthe value is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, but it being this big will\Nattract people's attention, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we run into bad thieves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a point. If we change it\Nto bills, we can all carry them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Your remark had a sting to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like me carrying it is a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You might drop it somewhere or lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he would. It's Luffy we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You guys! Don't you trust me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Nope!\N--Ah... Ahh... Ahh... That really hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to recover from thi-- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the only entrance to the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A rental bull shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they rent out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "bull"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me. Bulldogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Please let us rent bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask what they are first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome! You wanna rent bulls, right?\NHow many are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of bulls would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There're three ranks.\N"Yagara," "Rabuka," and "King."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for the three of you,\Ntwo Yagaras would probably do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Please roast them nice and tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird! That conversation is weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You followed logs to get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yep.\N--That's quite an achievement, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you had no idea what bulls were, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Right.\N--Well, to make a long\Nstory short, those are bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Yagara bulls.\NThey're everywhere in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In this area, there's a fish called\NYagara that swims with its head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the city of water.\NThere're more canals than walkways.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So bulls are a means of transportation\Nnecessary to the residents here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same when you go\Nsightseeing on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That fish is pulling a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than pulling, they're letting\Npeople ride on their back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's like horseback riding\Nor riding in a carriage on land...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the fish pen there?\NWell, try and ride on it. It's comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be 2,000 Berries for two\Ntwo-passenger Yagara bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fish that looks like a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk! What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? He must like you. Let's get him for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he carry heavy stuff okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Their power is incredible!\NYou can even use them for moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That bag, huh? What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're funny. Whatever it is, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--See?\N--Whoa! Give me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awfully honest old guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You too! Don't show it to others so lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? It wouldn't hurt, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my... What a surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then... it'll be a million\NBerries for two Yagara bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the price went up, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It'll be five million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It went up even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... We can't be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, 2,000 Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, are there any\Nmoney-changing shops around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there are, but with that amount of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the shops around here probably\Nwouldn't have enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go to the downtown\Narea of the shipbuilding island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The downtown area of the\Nshipbuilding island? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over there. Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A map?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be helpful! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, is the shipyard there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The world's No. 1 shipyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect. Once we get the money,\Nwe can go to the shipyard right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We can finally have\Nthe Going Merry repaired!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll find a shipwright, too!\NI'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,--Well, then...\N--Shall we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Go! Yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your business! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash to the shipyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
