Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that such a\Nconvenient creature exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't rock much. It's comfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! The canals even go above the rooftops!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such a huge town before!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. This is a town built around canals!
